FBIS3-32009 "drlat021_m_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-021 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Feb 1994 Brazil Latest Survey Shows Lula Leading Presidential Race PY3101220194 Rio de Janeiro O GLOBO in Portuguese 31 Jan 94 p 3 PY3101220194 Rio de Janeiro O GLOBO Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] The figures of the latest survey commissioned by the PSDB [Brazilian Social Democracy Party] by IBOPE [Brazilian Public Opinion and Statistics Institute] show that Lula [Inacio da Silva] dropped two points, [Antonio] Britto passed [Paulo] Maluf, [Leonel] Brizola's rating did not change, [Mario] Covas and Fernando Henrique Cardoso are in fourth place, and [Orestes] Quercia is in fifth place. Lula................28 percent Britto..............14 percent Maluf...............13 percent Brizola.............10 percent Covas................8 percent Cardoso..............8 percent Quercia..............5 percent
